            "client": "website",
            "content": "<p>I think that either super long-term partners (because they have a vested interest in helping you) or super short-term acquaintances (stranger on subway unlikely to run into again and hence unbiased oracles) are the only folks I'm really super interested in oversharing with.</p>",
