            "content": "<p>A friend is contemplating breaking up with their romantic partner, and asked me for advice about the situation. In this case, I don't have a strong feeling that they should or shouldn't either way, so I don't have a lot of useful advice to give them without having more of a conversation about the details of the situation.</p>\n<p>Are there any resources that you'd recommend to someone in this situation? What things have helped you make decisions like this?</p>\n<p>(personally, I don't see \"break up\"/\"not break up\" as a binary thing, but I think that's not super useful advice for people who are used to thinking about relationships in those terms, so that's what I'm aiming this post at)</p>",
