            "content": "<p>These are kind of intense, but they are the things that helped me the most in my life re: relationships:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://therumpus.net/2011/02/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-64/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://therumpus.net/2011/02/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-64/\">https://therumpus.net/2011/02/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-64/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://therumpus.net/2011/06/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-77-the-truth-that-lives-there/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://therumpus.net/2011/06/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-77-the-truth-that-lives-there/\">https://therumpus.net/2011/06/dear-sugar-the-rumpus-advice-column-77-the-truth-that-lives-there/</a></p>\n<p>And Scarleteen, as usual, seems to have some really awesome stuff to say on the subject of love:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.scarleteen.com/article/relationships/should_i_stay_or_should_i_go\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.scarleteen.com/article/relationships/should_i_stay_or_should_i_go\">https://www.scarleteen.com/article/relationships/should_i_stay_or_should_i_go</a></p>",
