        {
            "avatar_url": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4d074af6cc341ef51b25bb2f738cdb11?d=identicon&version=1",
            "client": "website",
            "content": "<p>I was wondering what people think about attachment styles? I read about them a couple of years ago and it was really eye-opening for me, and I made <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"25795\" href=\"/#narrow/stream/25795-beanbags/topic/attachment.20styles\">#beanbags &gt; attachment styles</a> about it, but I imagine people here have different/more varied perspectives now!</p>",
