        {
            "avatar_url": "https://zulip-avatars.s3.amazonaws.com/13/5d6a7a4735c43e9dae0e3f9ef82919706728452a?x=x&version=3",
            "client": "website",
            "content": "<p>i'm curious to hear what people think about this as well! i personally haven't found thinking about things in terms of attachment styles very useful for me (i guess i'm a dismissive-avoidant type?), but i know lots of people who find them really useful - if you're able to share, what was eye-opening about them for you?</p>",
